 Their first fight: Barry Stone, Jens Peermann and Patricia Rivera all phoned 
to say it could be a confrontational honeymoon inside that auto whose for-sale 
ad we published Wednesday. You may recall it was the car whose accessories 
included "fiance available." Anyway, they point out that the ad says the car 
also comes with "duel air." miscelLAny: 
