<P>
 Mark Woodforde of Australia, a surprise finalist in the Los Angeles Open two 
weeks ago, upset top-seeded Goran Ivanisevic, 6-3, 3-6, 7-5, in the RCA 
Championships at Indianapolis. 
</P>
<P>
