<TEXT>
<P>
 Re: "On the Cutting Edge -- Westside Veterinarians Are Leaders In High-Tech, 
High-Cost Pet Care" (July 31). 
</P>
<P>
 In addition to the doctors named in the article, there are also other 
veterinarians who should have been mentioned. They are all respected 
specialists in their particular field. One such example is Dr. Todd Tams of VCA 
West Los Angeles Animal Hospital. Dr. Tams is a world-renowned specialist in 
