</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "Sabor a Mexico," the annual downtown street fair, will take place Oct. 7-9 on 
Pacific Boulevard. 
</P>
<P>
 The salute to Mexican culture will include arts and crafts, exhibits, food 
booths, carnival rides and entertainment. 
</P>
